Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.85,0:00:05.90,Default - italics,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sunakawa Ai,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:07.82,Default - italics,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,a college freshman.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:09.82,Default - italics,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've gotten used to \Nliving on my own in Nagoya,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.14,0:00:13.54,Default - italics,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I went home for the first time in a \Nwhile, and I got quite a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:17.03,Default - italics,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo, of all people, now has a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:21.79,Default - italics,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, his girlfriend seems to \Nhave a secret she can't tell Takeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:25.90,Default - italics,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,And Takeo's starting to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:33.34,Phone,Sign 0031,0000,0000,0000,,Subject: Goodnight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:33.34,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun, I wonder if you're looking \Nat the Moon and the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:37.26,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a shooting star.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:39.97,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we can see a meteor \Nshower together someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.83,0:00:42.85,Message Body - Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.72,0:00:45.56,Message Body - Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:56.91,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Is Yamato trying too hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:01:00.31,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since we started dating,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:04.59,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I always end each day\N thinking it was a great day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.66,0:01:08.72,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato, don't hold it all in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:14.64,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to laugh at the\N end of each day, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:54.52,Title1,Sign 0250,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,513)}My Wish
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:07.91,Shuuei,Sign 0308,0000,0000,0000,,Shuuei High School
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:12.62,SignA,Sign 0309,0000,0000,0000,,Rose Kiss 2
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:16.74,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you reading shoujo manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:19.66,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just trying to learn as much \Nas I can about how girls think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:22.86,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to see Yamato-san today, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:25.89,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've got no such plans today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:28.02,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo! I recommend this one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.49,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,This is a real tearjerker!
