Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:31.23,Default,Kaki,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die from cuteness overload!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:32.90,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0330,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\c&H5D2ACA&}All Because of Love \N\NMy Boyfriend and Me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:35.14,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:36.52,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,She's a real stunner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.96,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,What's she doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:40.85,Default,Fudo,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she has a younger boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:43.00,Default,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll go say hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.84,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:07.60,Phone,Sign 0406,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Sunakawa Ai  \N\NNow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:07.60,Message Body - Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me and don't tell Takeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:13.36,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll go home early.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.36,0:04:15.92,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'm leaving once I finish this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:19.59,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'll text you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:22.49,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:25.14,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:29.66,Shuuei,Sign 0424,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Koizumi Girls' Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:28.13,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Takeo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:29.66,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:34.16,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I'd like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:41.67,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Yamato-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:44.05,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,You're hiding something \Nfrom Takeo, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.26,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:47.43,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo's noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:50.42,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,He knows you're hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.42,0:04:55.78,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,But because he doesn't know what \Nit is, he's worried sick about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:04:57.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:58.46,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:00.38,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,You're having a hard \Ntime telling Takeo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:01.94,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say a word about it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:04.08,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:06.95,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I want Takeo to be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.78,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I need him to be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:15.10,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:18.21,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun is a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:22.81,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But me? To be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:33.72,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the good person \NTakeo-kun thinks I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:35.43,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 0533,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H162932&}I KNEW IT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:38.19,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:45.99,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun has really nice skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:48.19,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.19,0:05:50.70,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,He goes to sleep early and wakes up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:52.16,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,He's got great skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:57.92,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,And his eyebrows and sideburns really get to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:06:00.08,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're so wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:05.59,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,And his broad shoulders and nice pecs...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.38,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,They've got great form, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.70,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,They're so muscular.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:11.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,And his lips are so sexy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:13.73,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Hollywood type!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:15.81,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,You don't find many of them in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:17.77,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,His hands are so big, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.81,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,They make my heart race!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:20.93,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:22.40,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,They're very sexy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:25.05,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But Takeo-kun says
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:29.11,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,he won't lay a finger on me until I grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:35.91,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun seems to think that \NI'm really pure and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:37.16,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:45.84,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to cuddle, \Nand hold hands, and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:52.85,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm with him, \NI have impure thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:55.16,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But how can I tell him that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:57.60,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,If I did, he'd stop liking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:01.81,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, he'd definitely back off...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.07,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that's the case, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:14.23,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's more important to me that \NYamato's in knots about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:17.53,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:21.25,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Takeo isn't that fragile!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:24.31,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't back away, just because \Nof something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:28.38,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,He's the kind of man who'll try to accept \Nyou head-on, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:30.99,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,He's dense and trusting,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:33.64,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't blame you for misreading him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:35.81,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,but Takeo told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:37.21,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "If Yamato won't tell me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:39.14,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I won't have a clue."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:42.14,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,But he also said he'd help, \Nif only you'd tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:45.90,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:51.06,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go over to his place right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:52.77,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Go now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:53.74,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:56.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:59.12,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good person!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:12.41,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo's girlfriend is a nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:14.07,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,They're happy together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:19.35,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy for Takeo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:23.55,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you fall for Takeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:27.94,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Remember the Growing Child statue
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:30.69,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,in the elementary-school yard?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:31.80,Shuuei,Sign 0831,0000,0000,0000,,Growing Child
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:33.45,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the creepy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:36.57,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I was tall and skinny,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:39.65,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,so guys started saying I looked like the statue,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:42.20,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,and gave me the nickname "Growing Statue."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:45.02,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,It did a number on my self-confidence as a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:48.50,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,But when I was in sixth grade,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:51.34,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo, who was in third grade at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.54,0:08:54.78,Default - flashback,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo, you're done with practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:55.84,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:58.53,Default - flashback,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,You can have half.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:00.72,Default - flashback,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,You must be thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:09.48,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,You remind me of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:11.44,Default - flashback,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the statue, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:12.44,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:16.42,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's that thing in the flower shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:18.12,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what it's called,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.34,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,but you remind me of that flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:22.49,Default - flashback,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:28.22,Default - flashback,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm that pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:29.25,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:33.97,Default - flashback,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm that pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:45.32,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:47.41,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:50.38,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,It might seem like nothing special \Nto others, but it's special to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:52.41,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it's like to fall in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:54.02,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:55.56,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,How could I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:57.10,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,We were three grades apart \Nin elementary school!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:58.30,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a first-year in high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:09:59.38,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,he was a first-year in junior high!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:00.74,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Junior high!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:05.62,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought he'd start dating someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:07.64,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he would.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:08.93,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,He's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:10.20,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:13.79,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,But I was hoping it'd at least \Ntake him until college!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:17.55,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But age difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:20.24,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You just said he isn't the type
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:22.72,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,to worry about something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:34.14,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:59.27,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Takeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:00.86,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:03.10,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The cat was having trouble getting out of a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.98,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato-san's headed for your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:10.35,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,She was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:13.98,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:15.91,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,was crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:29.26,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:33.65,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I was trying too hard to hide my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:38.50,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't trying hard enough to win Takeo over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:41.97,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd told him,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:48.10,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,maybe he would've run that fast for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:51.10,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,He would've.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:57.79,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:12:00.20,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I'd been born a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:01.36,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:04.91,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,You can stay friends with him forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.91,SFX-BlackWhite,Sign 1202,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs16\c&H505247&}What a pain-in-the-butt sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:18.46,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a fast runner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:20.04,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I was in the judo club,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.04,0:12:22.31,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I came in first three years in a row
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:24.71,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,in my junior high school's marathon,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:26.64,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,beating track and field, soccer, \Nand basketball guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:30.84,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I have endurance, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:32.81,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I'm a fast runner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:35.81,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I can run for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:42.81,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:54.25,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:02.00,EyecatchA,Sign 1301,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HCFCEA9&}Sweat
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:03.97,EyecatchB,Sign 1303,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD2CDA4&}Tears
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:13.48,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna said you were crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:16.59,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:22.99,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You ran all the way here for me, Takeo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:24.24,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:31.24,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:33.73,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,you've been troubled by something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:36.23,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:38.27,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me everything you're thinking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:40.07,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hit me with all you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:43.71,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I won't keel over, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:45.47,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,And laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:49.22,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I love seeing you laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:52.69,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.91,0:14:00.86,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hold hands with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:04.84,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:08.36,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I do want to snuggle and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:17.62,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm not as pure a \Ngirl as you thought I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything else you'd like to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:36.39,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maybe I'd like to walk with \Nyou like this for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:37.23,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:54.12,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we can go to a nearby park.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:54.87,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:24.64,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:26.79,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,My hand's sweating a ton!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:28.09,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:32.03,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yamato,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:34.61,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,am I correct in thinking that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.61,0:15:37.29,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,if I want to hold your hand, \NI don't need to hold back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:38.72,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:40.41,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Then don't hold back, either, Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:41.70,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:44.70,Default - flashback,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,She's a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:46.92,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's a very nice person!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:51.76,Default - flashback,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do you like \Nabout Yamato-san, Takeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:55.10,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's pure-hearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:05.67,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Takeo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:10.79,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Remember how, the day after we met, \NI went over to your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:13.36,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I know I said I'd asked around at the station,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:15.37,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but I lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:21.29,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I knew from your uniform that \Nyou went to Shuuei High School,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:24.58,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,so I went there and asked around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:29.82,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,And about how I forgot my cell in your room...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:31.59,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That was on purpose, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:33.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It was?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:37.41,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I wouldn't see you again \Nif I didn't have a reason, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:40.06,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I just had to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:45.49,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You said I was a good person, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:47.19,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.57,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:50.82,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:53.82,Shuuei,Sign 1652,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Shuuei
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:55.69,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,She went through a lot of trouble to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:05.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:08.63,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:15.67,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy you said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:19.57,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared that if I told you the truth, \Nyou wouldn't like me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:23.63,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I'm relieved, I guess I'm crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:27.40,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:29.69,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:33.18,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,When I got out of the fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:35.65,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I swore a vow to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:38.03,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,that I'd never make you cry again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:41.16,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:42.19,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,This is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:44.19,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,These are happy tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:47.10,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,So you can't count them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:55.52,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Think you can go to sleep smiling tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:57.58,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.58,0:18:01.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll probably be grinning ear to ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:09.94,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:12.39,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:16.61,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:19.05,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're okay with all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:19.89,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:23.62,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to rush back, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:25.83,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,This was for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:28.37,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I now know that Takeo's a happy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:34.24,Default,Ai,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want him to see \Nme like this, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:13.46,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo-kun, the stars are beautiful today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:16.59,Phone,Sign 1915,0000,0000,0000,,Subject: Shooting Star
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:16.59,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I saw my first-ever shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:20.31,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to be thinking about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:23.63,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,so I made a wish that I could \Nstay with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:25.56,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,By then, the star had already gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:26.90,Message Body - Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but maybe I made my wish in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.23,Message Body - Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:35.98,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:41.42,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Suna,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:43.32,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:54.83,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:56.63,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:00.26,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let me kiss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:03.14,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:06.20,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I held hands with Yamato today,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:07.89,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,but I kind of failed at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:11.87,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell do you fail at holding hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:15.38,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat the details!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:19.86,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,When we kiss, I wouldn't want \Nmy teeth to hit hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.23,0:20:24.03,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let me practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.56,0:20:26.72,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you practice with a pillow—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:28.12,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I already tried that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:31.27,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't get a good sense \Nof distance with a pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:33.12,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I need a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:34.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Try someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.85,0:20:37.46,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be an insult to Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:41.68,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at keeping secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:44.39,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of anyone else I can ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:47.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Quit it. It's gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:48.46,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:50.19,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I brought plastic wrap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:51.48,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, you're crossing a line...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:54.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,If we use this between, there's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:55.88,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, it's a huge problem—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:59.27,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm resolved to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:01.36,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You should be, too, \Nif you call yourself a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:05.11,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, there's something wrong \Nwith your logic for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:26.09,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:29.07,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become a man you can depend on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:31.77,SignB,Sign 2128,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on Our First Hand-Holding
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:31.77,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, go to sleep \Nwith a smile on your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:51.05,Title2,Sign 2247,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}My Strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.82,0:22:49.11,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: My Strength.
